For lack of a better idea, Phoenix innocently follows them.  The 
battered femme dearly hopes this will put some distance between her 
and Skullertron, who strikes her as supremely repulsive.

OOC: Phoenix is good at not drawing attention to herself, and wary of 
getting involved in conversations that don't directly concern her.  
(After more or less nine years of being beaten almost at random, you 
would be too.)  Hence her lack of contribution to discussions up 
until now.
